Have you got printed Devi’s names?

00:57:04.591 --> 00:57:08.126
Gavin, have you got copies?

00:57:10.246 --> 00:57:12.175
You have got them?

00:57:12.376 --> 00:57:16.158
Have you got these with you? Do you
have booklets?

